8/113482_mini.png?m=1497012181"},{"id":815016,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","description":"<p>有人问一个开源视频网站代码能不能给帮忙改改</p>\n<p>看了一眼 知乎好家伙</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://gitee.com/positive-rain-cloud/zy-film-admin/blob/master/public/api.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://gitee.com/positive-rain-cloud/zy-film-admin/blob/master/public/api.php</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/815016","replies":44,"created_ts":1636711456,"created":"18:04:16","title":"现如今的开源代码请谨慎使用","author":"dzdh","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dzdh","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1683/7ebf/226307_mini.png?m=1619139513"},{"id":814983,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"<p>比如 qq 音乐，优酷 youtube 等等</p>\n<p>网站（软件）本身没啥技术含量， 谁都写的出， 但背后的数据，可不是谁都能拥有</p>\n<p>==</p>\n<p>要么类似 pycharm ，Photoshop ，word 这种大型的，复杂软件</p>\n<p>要么就是 软件本身简单，但 背后的数据普通人难以获取，如 qq 音乐的歌曲库， 优酷的视频资源， </p>\n<p>大概就只有这两类， 能生存的比较好</p>\n<p>对吧？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/814983","replies":44,"created_ts":1636704466,"created":"16:07:46","title":"其实很多软件都没啥技术含量，背后的公司之所以赚钱，就是他们有数据，对吧？","author":"find456789","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/find456789","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d467f3b1603e9ceb12ff120c3a295919?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":814913,"node":"云计算","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/cloud","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_mini.png?m=1635654709","description":"<p>3 年 198 ，1 年 66 ，一个月 5.5 元，按一个月 30 天计算，一天约等于 0.2 元</p>\n<p>0.2 元什么概念，按照一度电 0.7 元来算的话，这是 0.3 度电差不多</p>\n<p>这个主机是 24 小时联网在线，这么算的话，别说赚钱，本钱都是亏的。</p>\n<p>我自己是买了，官网买可以退款。</p>\n<p>一年就这双十一有 3 年的配置买了，平时只有 1 年的可以买。</p>\n<p>如果你觉得我提供的信息靠谱，你可以请我恰饭</p>\n<p>我自己买的测试结果： <a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/QHOV7ir\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://imgur.com/a/QHOV7ir</a></p>\n<p>AFF 恰饭链接： <a href=\"https://ddl.ink/hqU5\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://ddl.ink/hqU5</a> （官网）</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/814913","replies":38,"created_ts":1636692235,"created":"12:43:55","title":"我给你们算下腾讯云 3 年 198 的服务器是什么概念","author":"manmamen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/manmamen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e25b0b7544ee8c3d317918c1298d3bed?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":814994,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1636254038","description":"<p>用来看的是  指电脑就是拿来看的，有更新了就升级，去尝个鲜，就玩个新鲜感。\n不干事就是  那种只打个网页，逛逛论坛、看看斗鱼虎牙这种。\n干点事的     就是要办个公，写个代码这种。</p>\n<p>我建议这 3 种人都不要升级 11 ，因为尝鲜都没啥可尝的，真好奇的话，弄个虚拟机体验一下吧。\n我还是太年轻，把自己的电脑升级了 11 ，现在一把辛酸泪，充满了后悔，不知道为啥，也不能回滚，唉。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/814994","replies":37,"created_ts":1636705875,"created":"16:31:15","title":"如果你的电脑用来看的就可以升级，但凡有点事干就别升 11","author":"Aaron01","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Aaron01","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0187/67b8/459229_mini.png?m=1635919246"},{"id":814978,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1635654575","description":"<p>最近几天看到大伙儿都在安利，价格也实惠，就入手了一台。\n之前用联通宽带有公网 IP ，新租的房有移动宽带，就没续费了。</p>\n<p>昨天服务器到手就折腾了 frp + wireguard ，整了好久（第一次玩这个，不是太懂），</p>\n<p>家里一台 linux 主机通过做 frp 客户端接入云主机的 frp ，因为部分服务没有密码保护，所以让服务映射监听在 wireguard 的接口上。在外面用 wireguard 连到云主机就能访问服务了。</p>\n<p>这样是常规操作吗，ssh frp 都改了默认端口，会有安全隐患吗？大伙儿是怎么弄的？</p>\n<p>现在没公网 IP ，bt 下载不稳定，有的资源一直没速度，能不能通过 frp 手段把端口映射到云服务器上，达到加速的目的？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/814978","replies":26,"created_ts":1636704042,"created":"16:00:42","title":"迫于买了 189 的云服务器, 求教远程回家方案","author":"lc1450","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lc1450","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fe12/653e/147664_mini.png?m=1468978054"},{"id":815043,"node":"iOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ios","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_mini.png?m=1611468295","description":"<p>晚上开暗黑模式刷了下知乎，切出去回条消息，回来就是个广告，太特么恶心了，比开屏广告还恶心，由于触发时机不确定，还不那么好抓 url ，有哪位抓住过这广告的 url 吗，我要把它屏蔽了！！！</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/815043","replies":25,"created_ts":1636723245,"created":"21:20:45","title":"知乎 for ios 切屏广告问题","author":"DShen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/DShen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/81fa/6f7d/509034_mini.png?m=1600668638"},{"id":815010,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933","description":"<p><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/IDhWXq\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"IDhWXq.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/11/12/IDhWXq.png\"/></a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/815010","replies":22,"created_ts":1636709659,"created":"17:34:19","title":"mbp14 寸定制版，居然提前准备发货了！","author":"hengo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hengo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a78b/4707/282179_mini.png?m=1612331843"}]